<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Your BeOrchid Super Admin credentials</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px;">
  <h1 style="color: #2e7d32;">Welcome to BeOrchid, {{firstName}}!</h1>
  <p>Your <strong>super_admin</strong> account has been created on the BeOrchid platform.</p>
  <p>Here are your login credentials:</p>
  <table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin: 16px 0;">
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px 12px; background: #f5f5f5; font-weight: bold; width: 120px;">Email</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px 12px;">{{email}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px 12px; background: #f5f5f5; font-weight: bold;">Password</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px 12px; font-family: monospace; font-size: 16px;">{{password}}</td>
    </tr>
  </table>
  <p style="color: #c62828;"><strong>Important:</strong> Please change your password immediately after your first login.</p>
  <p>This email was generated automatically. If you did not expect it, please contact your system administrator.</p>
  <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0; margin: 24px 0;" />
  <p style="color: #9e9e9e; font-size: 12px;">BeOrchid &mdash; Precision Farming &amp; AgriMarket Platform</p>
</body>
</html>
